1. get the current academic year from the site, this is done in the background, 
  the user doesn't handle this.

2. function that returns semester selection options for the current academic year
get_semesters()

3. function that returns category selection options for the selected semester
get_categories(semester_id)

4. function that returns download options for the selected category
get_download_options(semester_id, category_id)

5. function that returns data for the selected download option
get_data(semester_id, category_id, download_option_id)

6. function that returns the timetable given the above correct item ids
get_timetable(semester_id, category_id, download_option_id, data_id)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

supportive functions

1. function that returns the current academic year
get_current_academic_year()

2. function to fetch data from the web given a url with paramters,
  this function should have appropriate error handling techniques
fetch_data(url)
